<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/OpenIMSDK/Open-IM-iOS-Demo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open-IM-iOS-Demo<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>: An iOS demo based on Open-IM-SDK-iOS, available for developers to reference.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/OpenIMSDK/Open-IM-Android-Demo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open-IM-Android-Demo<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>: An Android demo based on Open-IM-SDK-Android, available for developers to reference.</li>
